WEBVTT

00:11:29.128 --> 00:11:31.253
for all businesses,

00:11:31.253 --> 00:11:32.920
all businesses benefit

00:11:32.920 --> 00:11:35.651
yet all can compete.

00:11:35.651 --> 00:11:37.372
Now the orthodox reaction, of course,

00:11:37.372 --> 00:11:41.175
is raising the minimum wage costs jobs. Right?

00:11:41.175 --> 00:11:43.763
Your politician's always echoing

00:11:43.763 --> 00:11:46.855
that trickle-down idea by saying things like,

00:11:46.855 --> 00:11:48.948
"Well, if you raise the price of employment,

00:11:48.948 --> 00:11:51.740
guess what happens? You get less of it."

00:11:51.740 --> 00:11:54.170
Are you sure?

00:11:54.170 --> 00:11:57.823
Because there's some contravening evidence.

00:11:57.823 --> 00:12:02.582
Since 1980, the wages of CEOs in our country